import './EditProfile.css'; import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import { Link, useParams, useHistory } from 'react-router-dom'; import profileimg from '../assets/profile.jpg'; import { useAuth0 } from '@auth0/auth0-react'; import axios from 'axios'; function EditProfile() { axios.defaults.baseURL = "http://localhost:3001"; const history = useHistory(); const { user } = useAuth0(); const { email } = useParams(); const [successMsg, setSuccessMsg] = useState(false); const [userInfo, setUserInfo] = useState([]); useEffect(() => { axios.get('/users/' + user.name) .then(res =>{ if(res.data != null) {setUserInfo(res.data)}}) .catch(err => console.log(err)); }, [user.name]); const onSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault() axios.put('/users/edit/' + user.name, userInfo) .then((res) => { setSuccessMsg(true) console.log(res.data) }).catch((error) => { console.log(error) }); } return (
setUserInfo({...userInfo, username: e.target.value})}/>
